OL,3,CTrump presidency has brought Britain
OL,4,Cand Canada even closer, envoy says
OL,6,FBy Westminster Reporter Lewis Denison
OL,7,Fand Producer Sarika Gandhi
OL,9,FBritain and Canada have the world's
OL,10,Fclosest relationship and Donald
OL,11,FTrump's presidency has "in many ways"
OL,12,Fallowed them to get even closer, the
OL,13,FCanadian High Commissioner to the UK
OL,14,Fhas said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
