CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778170273
OL,3,CTrump presidency has brought Britain
OL,4,Cand Canada even closer, envoy says
OL,6,FBill Blair, who was appointed High
OL,7,FCommissioner in March, told ITV News
OL,8,Fin an exclusive interview that despite
OL,9,Fthe "special relationship" label and
OL,10,Fhis country's geographic proximity to
OL,11,FAmerica, it is the UK and Canada who
OL,12,Fare "joined more than any other two
OL,13,Fcountries in the world".
OL,15,FHe added that our shared head of
OL,16,Fstate, King Charles, is a source of
OL,17,Fpride for Canadians who has reminded
OL,18,Fthem to love their country.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
