PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778170273
OL,3,CTrump presidency has brought Britain
OL,4,Cand Canada even closer, envoy says
OL,6,FBlair, whose role is equivalent to
OL,7,Fthat of an ambassador but for
OL,8,Fcountries in the Commonwealth, spoke
OL,9,Fto ITV News for his first sit-down
OL,10,Finterview since taking up post.
OL,12,F'UK and Canada closer than any other
OL,13,Fcountries in the world'
OL,15,FSince Trump's return to the White
OL,16,FHouse in 2025, the UK's and Canada's
OL,17,Fclose relationship with the US has
OL,18,Fbeen tested.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778170273
OL,3,CTrump presidency has brought Britain
OL,4,Cand Canada even closer, envoy says
OL,6,FTrump has repeatedly publicly
OL,7,Fcriticised UK Prime Minister Keir
OL,8,FStarmer and even threatened to make
OL,9,FCanada the 51st American state.
OL,11,FThat threat, plus trade tariffs
OL,12,Fimposed on Canada, led Prime Minister
OL,13,FMark Carney to seek closer
OL,14,Fpartnerships with others, including
OL,15,Fthe UK and the European Union.
OL,17,FHigh Commissioner Blair said the UK
OL,18,Fand Canada are "actually joined more
OL,19,Fthan any other two countries in the
OL,20,Fworld".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778170273
OL,3,CTrump presidency has brought Britain
OL,4,Cand Canada even closer, envoy says
OL,6,FThe centuries-old relationship, which
OL,7,Fbegan with Britain becoming "one of
OL,8,Fthe founding nations" of Canada, has
OL,9,Finvolved both countries fighting two
OL,10,Fworld wars together, being part of the
OL,11,FUN, Nato, G20, and G7, as well as the
OL,12,FCommonwealth.
OL,14,FCarney was governor of the Bank of
OL,15,FEngland before becoming prime minister
OL,16,Fand both countries share a head of
OL,17,Fstate in King Charles.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778170273
OL,3,CTrump presidency has brought Britain
OL,4,Cand Canada even closer, envoy says
OL,6,FHigh Commissioner Blair said Donald
OL,7,FTrump's presidency has "in many ways"
OL,8,Fallowed the UK and Canada to come
OL,9,Fcloser together.
OL,11,FTrump's claim that Canada could be
OL,12,Fannexed to become America's 51st state
OL,13,Freminded Canadians "that we love our
OL,14,Fcountry", he said.
OL,16,F"But he also reminded us that we have
OL,17,Fa responsibility to our own
OL,18,Fsovereignty, to our own security, to
OL,19,Finvest in ourselves," he added.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
