CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778170273
OL,3,CTrump presidency has brought Britain
OL,4,Cand Canada even closer, envoy says
OL,6,FNot long after Trump threatened
OL,7,FCanada's sovereignty, King Charles
OL,8,Fbecame the first monarch since 1957 to
OL,9,Fpreside over the opening of a new
OL,10,FCanadian parliament.
OL,12,F'King Charles makes Canadians proud'
OL,14,F"It was a very important moment for
OL,15,FCanadians," when King Charles gave a
OL,16,Fspeech opening their Parliament, the
OL,17,FHigh Commissioner said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
