PN,30708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778170273
OL,3,CTrump presidency has brought Britain
OL,4,Cand Canada even closer, envoy says
OL,6,F"It reinforced for Canadians as well
OL,7,Fthat he is our sovereign and that
OL,8,Fhelps define us as a constitutional
OL,9,Fmonarchy within the Commonwealth," he
OL,10,Fadded.
OL,12,FUnlike some countries in the
OL,13,FCommonwealth, which have been
OL,14,Fquestioning whether they want a
OL,15,Fforeign king as their head of state,
OL,16,FCanadians broadly support it, Mr Blair
OL,17,Ftold ITV News.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
