PN,30709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778170273
OL,3,CTrump presidency has brought Britain
OL,4,Cand Canada even closer, envoy says
OL,6,FAsked how the King is received in
OL,7,FCanada, he said: "Very positively. And
OL,8,Ffirst of all, the Queen, of course,
OL,9,Fwas beloved in Canada.
OL,11,F"But the King, I think, provided that
OL,12,Fcontinuity, that of the role that the
OL,13,Fmonarchy has and the fact that he is
OL,14,Ftruly our king, the head of state of
OL,15,Four country. And it's a source of
OL,16,Fpride us."
OL,18,FWhen King Charles recently attended
OL,19,Fthe US for a state visit, he delivered
OL,20,Ftwo speeches in which he made subtle
OL,21,Fsuggestions to President Trump.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
