PN,30710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778170273
OL,3,CTrump presidency has brought Britain
OL,4,Cand Canada even closer, envoy says
OL,6,FIn one joke, he gently reminded Trump
OL,7,Fhe was head of state of Canada, so the
OL,8,Fpair would be "joint hosts" of the
OL,9,FFootball World Cup.
OL,11,FThe two speeches delivered by King
OL,12,FCharles, one to Congress and another
OL,13,Fduring a state banquet, were widely
OL,14,Fpraised for their humour and diplomacy
OL,15,Fby Brits who felt proud to watch.
OL,26,@pD@OOUpD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/20
