OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778170273
OL,3,CTrump presidency has brought Britain
OL,4,Cand Canada even closer, envoy says
OL,6,FHigh Commissioner Blair said he was
OL,7,F"certain" Canadians felt that same
OL,8,Fpride, adding that the speeches "made
OL,9,Fa very strong point to Canadians - and
OL,10,FI would hope to our American friends -
OL,11,Fthat we are an independent, sovereign
OL,12,Fnation".
OL,14,FCanada and the New World Order
OL,16,FTrump's behaviour in his second
OL,17,Fpresidency have led smaller nations to
OL,18,Freconsider whether America is a
OL,19,Freliable partner, both on trade and
OL,20,Fdefence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
