OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778170273
OL,3,CTrump presidency has brought Britain
OL,4,Cand Canada even closer, envoy says
OL,6,FHe's hit close allies such as Canada
OL,7,Fand the UK with trade tariffs,
OL,8,Fthreatened to pull out Nato and even
OL,9,Fcalled the alliance a "paper tiger"
OL,10,Fwhich would be unable to defend itself
OL,11,Fwithout American support.
OL,13,FAmid the uncertainty, Prime Minister
OL,14,FCarney has talked about a new world
OL,15,Forder which would be rebuilt around
OL,16,FEurope rather than the US.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778170273
OL,3,CTrump presidency has brought Britain
OL,4,Cand Canada even closer, envoy says
OL,6,F"It has created an opportunity not
OL,7,Fjust for Canada, but for all of the
OL,8,Fmiddle powers to focus on what is
OL,9,Frequired for our prosperity in the
OL,10,Ffuture," High Commissioner Blair said.
OL,12,FHe added: "The role that America
OL,13,Fchooses to assume in the free world
OL,14,Fis, is clearly, is clearly changing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30714
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778170273
OL,3,CTrump presidency has brought Britain
OL,4,Cand Canada even closer, envoy says
OL,6,F"And I think it also creates a
OL,7,Fresponsibility for others to step up
OL,8,Finto their place. I think as well, the
OL,9,FPrime Minister (Carney) recognises the
OL,10,Fascendancy of Europe, the importance
OL,11,Fof Europe and our long standing
OL,12,Frelationship our European allies as a
OL,13,Fmember of Nato.
OL,15,F"We're not a European nation, but the
OL,16,Frelationships we have with Europe, and
OL,17,FI think the Prime Minister's intimate
OL,18,Funderstanding and knowledge of that
OL,19,Frelationship is something that he
OL,20,Fcertainly has promoted and we very
OL,21,Fmuch support."
