OL,3,CTrump presidency has brought Britain
OL,4,Cand Canada even closer, envoy says
OL,6,FAntisemitism in the UK, Canada and the
OL,7,FWest
OL,9,FAs a former police officer with four
OL,10,Fdecades experience, 10 years of which
OL,11,Fwere spent as Toronto's chief of
OL,12,Fpolice, Blair was also asked about
OL,13,Frising antisemitism.
OL,15,FHe said is not just a problem in
OL,16,FBritain, it is a "challenge" for the
OL,17,Fwhole Western world, adding that the
OL,18,Fwars in Gaza and Iran have led to a
OL,19,Frise in "the oldest form of hate".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30716
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778170273
OL,3,CTrump presidency has brought Britain
OL,4,Cand Canada even closer, envoy says
OL,6,F"All of us are struggling with how do
OL,7,Fwe stand up to hatred - and hatred, I
OL,8,Fthink, is the greatest enemy of our
OL,9,Fsocieties," he said.
OL,11,F"It crosses over into the promulgation
OL,12,Fof hate and violence against innocent
OL,13,Fpeople," he said, adding: "That's
OL,14,Fcompletely unacceptable. And I think
OL,15,Fall police services across the Western
OL,16,Fworld are facing that challenge."
OL,18,FIn the UK, 63% of Britons say
OL,19,Fantisemitism is a major or significant
OL,20,Fproblem in British society, a new poll
OL,21,Fby YouGov has suggested.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
