PN,30717
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778170273
OL,3,CTrump presidency has brought Britain
OL,4,Cand Canada even closer, envoy says
OL,6,FThe poll comes after a series of arson
OL,7,Fattacks at Jewish sites in London, as
OL,8,Fwell as a double stabbing in Golders
OL,9,FGreen last week that is being treated
OL,10,Fas an act of terrorism.
OL,12,FOn Wednesday, the Met Police said the
OL,13,Fnumber of antisemitic hate crimes
OL,14,Frecorded last month was the highest in
OL,15,Ftwo years. Some 140 offences were
OL,16,Flogged across the capital in April, up
OL,17,Ffrom 98 in March and 67 in February,
OL,18,Faccording to new data published by the
OL,19,Fforce.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30718
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778170273
OL,3,CTrump presidency has brought Britain
OL,4,Cand Canada even closer, envoy says
OL,6,FHigh Commissioner Blair said all
OL,7,Fsocieties need to "stand up strongly"
OL,8,Fto antisemitism - and part of the
OL,9,Fsolution is to crack down on protests
OL,10,Fthat cross the "threshold into hatred".
OL,12,FStarmer has resisted pressure from
OL,13,FLeader of the Opposition Kemi Badenoch
OL,14,Fand Jewish groups to ban pro-Palestine
OL,15,Fmarches, which often take place in
OL,16,FLondon, but promised in the wake of
OL,17,Fthe Golders Green attack that they
OL,18,Fwill be policed more strongly.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30719
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778170273
OL,3,CTrump presidency has brought Britain
OL,4,Cand Canada even closer, envoy says
OL,6,FAsked if those protests should be
OL,7,Fbanned, Mr Blair said: "There's a
OL,8,Fline. Lawful peaceful protest is a
OL,9,Fright in our society... And we need to
OL,10,Fdefend the right for freedom of
OL,11,Fprotest and expression of opinion.
OL,13,F"But when that crosses the threshold
OL,14,Finto hatred, the promotion of hatred
OL,15,Fand the advocacy of violence towards a
OL,16,Fpeople, then that's where of the
OL,17,Fcriminal offence is."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
